3G/4G/LTE Module
----------------

|Product| is equipped with a **mini-PCIe connector** that can connect to a 3G/4G module.
The customer will also need a SIM Card Holder and a 3G/4G Antenna Connector to ensure 3G/4G works on the |product|. SIM card does **NOT** support hot plug. **Power off** before inserting or removing SIM card.

.. rst-class:: text-center

    |sim_img|

    *SIM Card Direction*


.. figure:: /Media/Pi/A53/Others/4G_module.jpeg
   :align: center
   :figclass: align-center

   *3G/4G Module*


.. figure:: /Media/Pi/A53/Others/4G_com.jpeg
   :align: center
   :figclass: align-center

   *SIM Card Holder and 3G/4G Antenna Connector*


.. attention::

    The product does not come shipped with the 3G/4G module by default.